WEBVTT

00:02:29.995 --> 00:02:32.421
we believed that,

00:02:32.421 --> 00:02:34.680
if we were smart enough

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:39.011
and strong enough and brave enough,

00:02:39.011 --> 00:02:41.484
and we worked hard enough,

00:02:41.484 --> 00:02:46.762
we could keep him from dying ever.

00:02:46.762 --> 00:02:50.261
And for years, it seemed like we were succeeding.

00:02:50.261 --> 00:02:53.140
The surgeon emerged from the surgery.

00:02:53.140 --> 00:02:55.417
What'd he say? He said what surgeons always say:

00:02:55.417 --> 00:02:57.419
"We got it all."

